        {
            "title": "鍾培生淺水灣豪宅內求婚莊雅婷 5層高獨立屋面積逾萬呎 估值約20億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「百億富三代」<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:鍾培生;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鍾培生\">鍾培生</a>昨日（5日）宣布向現任西貢區議員莊雅婷求婚成功，引起全城熱議。他更於社交平台上載影片曝光求婚場面，片中可見求婚選址淺水灣鍾家大宅內進行，現場設有巨型場景佈置及管弦樂團伴奏，鍾培生更從大宅樓頂天台吊威也一躍而下，場面震撼。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該處大宅位於淺水灣南灣道4A，樓高5層，面積超過1萬呎。鍾培生曾於媒體訪問裡透露，同類屋苑呎價約2.2萬元，而其豪宅逾1萬呎，因此估計該大宅市值約20億元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QwG9l0Nf9ret54s6eU8PXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/b1a075655afc2c7d55ca34f42cda20b6\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過去曾有多家傳媒進入鍾家大宅採訪拍攝，從采訪片段可見，大宅裝修簡約以白色為主，樓底極高，一樓設有飯廳及客廳，面積約千呎。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-448d860d-c330-36cb-b051-126abe445f60-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4pkg8RdshBVxGZCO0Auqew--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/b96ebdb5b4b8b5cbe4bec24c9bcd73e2\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">客廳外面的花園分成兩層，放置了戶外餐枱餐椅，可容納幾十人開party，另一邊則設有鍾培生的專屬擂台。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/l3GPlr7kayskIqiOJuC6UQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/21004189f0a0df9892be605d59f3b24f\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，大宅內有麻雀房、酒窖、健身室、蒸氣室和超大衣帽間等眾多設施，天台擁有無敵靚海景。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:淺水灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/淺水灣-27326\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">淺水灣</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:西貢;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/西貢-27317\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">西貢</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E9%8D%BE%E5%9F%B9%E7%94%9F%E6%B7%BA%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E5%85%A7%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A%E8%8E%8A%E9%9B%85%E5%A9%B7-5%E5%B1%A4%E9%AB%98%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%8B%E9%9D%A2%E7%A9%8D%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%91%8E-%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC%E7%B4%8420%E5%84%84-74870\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8D%BE%E5%9F%B9%E7%94%9F%E6%B7%BA%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E5%85%A7%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A%E8%8E%8A%E9%9B%85%E5%A9%B7-5%E5%B1%A4%E9%AB%98%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%8B%E9%9D%A2%E7%A9%8D%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%91%8E-%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC%E7%B4%8420%E5%84%84-071608133.html",
